<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4607635>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Epipenaeon ingens Nobili, 1906, reference female (CIEPE541104) (A–I), reference male (CIEPE541104) (J-L). (A) Dorsal view; (B) Ventral view; (C) Right antennule and antenna; (D) Right maxilliped, external view; (E) Right side of barbula; (F) Right oostegite1, external view; (G) Right oostegite 1, internal view; (H) Right pereopod 1; (I) Left pereopod 7; (J) Dorsal view; (K) Ventral view; (L) Left antenna and antennule; Scale: 1mm for A, B; 0.08 mm for C, L; 0.33 mm for D; 0.27 mm for E, J, K; 0.60 mm for F, G; 0.21 mm for H, I." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4607635/files/figure.png" .
